# MANIFEST for coq-robust-predicates
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Source-of-record paths (relative to the NetTopologySuite.Proofs repo root)
# for every .v file vendored into this standalone package.  `assemble.sh`
# copies these into ./theories and ./theories-flocq, preserving the
# NTS.Proofs / NTS.Proofs.Flocq namespaces so no import statement needs
# editing.  This file is the single point of truth for the package's contents
# -- the .v files themselves are NOT committed here (they live in the corpus),
# so there is no risk of a vendored copy silently drifting from the original.
#
# Closure verified: this 15-file set is closed under intra-corpus imports
# (every `From NTS.Proofs[.Flocq] Require` resolves within the set); the only
# external dependencies are Rocq's Stdlib and Flocq.

